cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this artifact, please cite it and the accompanying DELFI 2026 paper."
title: "rse_in_delfi_artifact: A reproducible, database-free pipeline for detecting research-software paradigms in the DELFI community"
abstract: >-
  Replication/artifact package for the DELFI 2026 paper "Research Software
  Engineering in the Learning Technologies: a replication study of research
  paradigms in the DELFI community". Ships all intermediate products and a
  six-step, file-based pipeline that reproduces the label aggregation, ICR
  metrics, figures and secondary analysis without the copyrighted paper PDFs or
  an LLM API token. No paper full text is included.
